  }, 
  {
   "begin": "370.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "375.400", 
   "id": "s000121", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir m\u00fcssen die Arbeits\u00fcberlastung beim BGH auf jeden Fall beenden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "375.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "381.760", 
   "id": "s000122", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die obersten Gerichte m\u00fcssen in aller Ruhe \u00fcber die f\u00fcr die B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger wichtigen Fragen entscheiden k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "381.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "387.800", 
   "id": "s000123", 
